Italy's wholesale price index rise 0.5 pct month-on-month April increase 0.1 pct March statistic institute Istat said. The index base 1980 equal 100 register 174.2 April compare 173.3 March. The April figure represent increase 1.6 pct compare correspond month 1986 year-on-year rise March 0.6 pct. REUTER 